<br>
If you're 51 and have epic go nuts in some place like Lguk and have your pet kill anything that moves until you get a bunch of AA racked up.  If you find that you're getting AA slower than 1AA point every 3 hours or so then go to regular XP until you can hit the planes becuase then you'll get getting 1 AA every 2-3 hours or faster.<br>
